etting it sit ain't gonna cut it.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Third, peat and verm hydrate at different rates, so it's always best to moisten them separately and then mix.&amp;nbsp; Taking shortcuts until you know all the ropes is asking for failure. The casing layer tek was produced after doing this a few thousand times.&amp;nbsp; It wasn't designed to make you take unnecessary steps.&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>12361236</next>\n<prev>12361112</prev>\n<first>12355534</first>\n<last>12362842</last>\n<when>1270830530</when>\n<utime>04/09/10 07:28 PM</utime>\n</post>"}